==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Heirship
<hw>Heir"ship</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state,
character, or privileges of an heir; right of inheriting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Heirship movables</b></col>, <cd>certain kinds of
movables which the heir is entitled to take, besides the heritable
estate.</cd> <mark>[Scot.]</mark></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hejira</ent>⟦br⟧
